@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dapofk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.53 * v1 + 0.96)) * (0.35 - wp.exp(v0 + 0.92)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.42) / wp.cos(tmp + 0.75)) + ((v0 + 0.38 + v1 + 0.77) - v2))
    tmp = ((v2 - (tmp + 0.84 + tmp + 0.21)) + (wp.abs(v0 + 0.65) * tmp))
    tmp = (v1 + wp.abs(0.25))
    tmp = (wp.cos(tmp) + ((tmp + 0.60 - tmp + 0.99) - (tmp + 0.71 / v2 + 0.73)))
    v0 = 0.61
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.44) - (v2 + 0.16 * v1 + 0.45)) - v0)
    data[tid] = v0
